data.description: Channel responses follow the Activity Streams JSON specification (http://activitystrea.ms/specs/json/1.0/).  In its simplest form, an activity consists of an actor, a verb, an object and a target.  on genre channels the actor is “site”, the verb is “post”, the object is “track” and the target is implicit. on site channels, the actor will always be the same. List of channel keys Genre channels /channels/idm /channels/uk+garage Media channels MP3 tracks: /channels/media:mp3 YouTube tracks: /channels/media:youtube Vimeo tracks: /channels/media:vimeo SoundCloud tracks: /channels/media:soundcloud Official.fm tracks: /channels/media:officialfm Site channels /channels/site:37 Artist channels /channels/artist:419
